package com.telenav.mesakit.map.ui.desktop.graphics.canvas
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    MapProjection
    Maps between drawing coordinates, as expressed by Drawing* objects, and map coordinates, as expressed by Location, Latitude, Longitude, Rectangle Distance, Width, Height and Size.
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    MapCanvas
    A DrawingSurface with a MapCanvas.mapArea() and a MapCanvas.drawingSize() and a MapCanvas.projection() that maps between the two: MapCanvas.toDrawing(Location) MapProjection.toDrawing(Distance) MapProjection.toDrawing(Rectangle) MapProjection.toDrawing(Width) MapProjection.toDrawing(Height) MapCanvas.toDrawing(Size) MapCanvas.toMap(DrawingPoint) MapProjection.toMap(DrawingLength) MapProjection.toMap(DrawingRectangle) MapProjection.toMap(DrawingWidth) MapProjection.toMap(DrawingHeight) MapProjection.toMap(DrawingSize)
